{"tid":201686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【狗咬狗】九龍灣的士撼鐵馬 高級督察重傷命危","createTime":"2017-04-15T03:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T03:51:59.000Z","uid":36551,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03ba0c09774c54e26a0a374d51310d1d4ea2c388","tid":201686,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"九龍灣的士撼鐵馬 高級督察重傷命危<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0415 03:45<br />\n<br />\n一名高級督察凌晨執行職務時遇上車禍重創，目前情況危殆，留醫深切治療部。凌晨約3時22分，九龍灣宏照道與啟祥道交界，一輛由警方東九龍交通部高級督察駕駛的鐵馬執行任務，亮著燈沿宏照道往啟業邨方向行駛，另一輛的士則沿啟祥道往牛頭角。至交界燈位時疑有車衝燈，兩車發生相撞，的士攔腰猛撞向鐵馬，將其推上安全島及撞向鐵欄，的士車頭及鐵馬嚴重損毀。高級督察墮地頭手腳受傷，血流披面，送伊利沙伯醫院仍痛苦呻吟，搶救後情況危殆。50歲姓林的士司機協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n重傷高級督察姓張，53歲已婚，沒有子女，92年加入警隊，據悉他意外後有腦出血、骨折，但幸未有傷及內臟。<br />\n高級督察的家人及同袍事後到醫院深切治療部了解及守候。警方行動處處長鄧炳強將到醫院探望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170415/56567004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170415%2F56567004&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7pnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bc6bcc75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170415%2F56567004&h=f00f95a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170415/56567004</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceeb106d2336e3b3ebe476c443df1f33540daef","tid":201686,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:11:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a03bbee499fa8b2a6061612e07146a549466319a","tid":201686,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"比啲口德我！"},{"pid":"210a564e0aa3b17d0482ed143bf87de2f8f88697","tid":201686,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>